# API (tRPC)

- Add endpoints in `server/src/trpc/router.ts` only
- Validate inputs with Zod; use `publicProcedure` unless auth is added
- DB access via `ctx.prisma`, session via `ctx.sessionId`
- Export `AppRouter` type — client imports `@timetable/server/trpc`
- Client calls: `trpc.<namespace>.<procedure>.useQuery()` / `.useMutation()`
- Do not add REST routes or duplicate types on the client
